widgets.title: How many learners use the platform?
widgets.desc:
This chart displays the number of new and active users enrolled by month.
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: How long do learners spend studying?
widgets.desc:
This graph displays total hours spent in the platform and average hours per user.
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: Are learners happy with the platform?
widgets.desc:
This chart shows the total review count and average review score by month.
Click into the table view to read comments for each review.
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: How often do learners study?
widgets.desc:
This graph shows the average sessions per user and average session duration, by month.
Data source: Google Analytics

widgets.title: Are learners retained over time?
widgets.desc:
This heat map displays user retention over time. Each square indicates the % of users who were first active in a given month who remained active X months later.
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: Which device do learners use to study?
From what US states are learners studying?
widgets.desc:
This chart shows the number of sessions by US state in the last 90 days.
Data source: Google Analytics

widgets.title: How many exams do learners take?
widgets.desc:
This chart provides a total of exams started and completed, by month (including resets).
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: How do learners score on exams?
widgets.desc:
This chart provides the total exams completed and average exam score (including resets) for learners.
The data filters out any exams taken in less than 20 minutes to control for outliers.
Data source:

widgets.title: Which exam topics take learners the longest?
widgets.desc:
This boxplot displays a spread of time taken on exam questions, by topic.
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: With which exam questions do learners struggle?
widgets.desc:
This scatterplot shows average % correct for exam questions against the average time taken to answer each question. Each point is a unique exam question.
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: Which question topics do learners study the most?
widgets.desc:
This chart shows average answers per question in each category rather than total answers. It displays the number of correct and incorrect answers per question.
Data source: BenchPrep database

widgets.title: Does device type affect learner engagement?
widgets.desc:
This graph displays the % of questions answered between exam and practice question (including resets), by platform type.
Data source: BenchPrep database
